# .mcp-index-ignore
#
# Security configuration for Code Index MCP server to prevent indexing of sensitive files.
# Code Index MCP provides AST-based code analysis for better AI assistance, but should
# exclude files containing secrets, credentials, and other sensitive data.
#
# See: https://github.com/modelcontextprotocol/servers/tree/main/src/code-index
# Related: Issue #206

